<% content_for :application do %>
  <dismissable class="flash flash-notice">
    <p>
      Development of Jottings is on hold. The app is fully operational but runs
      on minimal setup which may cause synchronization lags. We decided to switch
      our focus to our other app called <a href="//coypu.co">Coypu</a>.
      A lot of things that we've learned here like operational transformations,
      contenteditable API, Vue.js and modern JS practices are helping us in
